#### serializeObject
`.serializeObject(form)`

###### Description:
Serialize form fields to json. It can be used as a data to the ajax function.

###### Sample:
``` js
define(['ajax'], function(ajax) {
	var serializedForm = ajax.serializeObject(document.querySelector('form'));
});
```


